{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s59jj/b/2/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t33/s59jj/b/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft33%2Fs59jj%2Fb%2F2%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"; andsection 1344 of this title","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"C","heading":null,"label":"C","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s59jj/b/2/C","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t33/s59jj/b/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft33%2Fs59jj%2Fb%2F2%2FC","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the National Environmental Policy Act of 1969 ( et seq.).42 U.S.C. 4321","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"c","heading":"Termination of designation","label":"c Termination of designation","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s59jj/c","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t33/s59jj","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft33%2Fs59jj%2Fc","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"If, on the date that is 20 years after , any area or portion of an area described in subsection (a)(3) is not bulkheaded, filled, or otherwise occupied by permanent structures (including marina facilities) in accordance with subsection (b), or if work in connection with any activity authorized under subsection (b) is not commenced by the date that is 5 years after the date on which permits for the work are issued, the designation of nonnavigability under subsection (a)(1) for that area or portion of an area shall terminate.November 12, 20014So in original. Probably should be “subsection (a)(2)”.4","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}
